            "id": "our-story-text",
            "elType": "widget",
            "widgetType": "text-editor",
            "settings": {
              "editor": "<p>Founded in {{founded}} by {{founder}}, {{name}} has been proudly serving {{city}}, {{state}} for over {{years_in_business}} years. What started as a small family business has grown into a trusted team of {{team_size}} dedicated professionals.</p><p>{{story}}</p><p>Today, we continue to uphold the same values that {{founder}} established from day one: exceptional service, honest pricing, and treating every customer like family.</p>",
